snippet.title: Dancing Stage Euromix 2 Song List
snippet.description:
European arcade mix and the sequel to DS Euromix. At least the banners aren't a generic blue banner.

I can't find a full DS Em1 song list.

Green songs - New licenses
Yellow songs - New Konami original songs
Blue songs - Returning Konami original songs
